name: Love Being A Lady
description:
Exclusive Chic Tee only found here!
A Lady is one with refined habits. She is classy, independent, well rounded and a joy to be around. She has pizzaz and knows what she wants. She knows when to lead and when to be led. She is a pioneer, a trendsetter, a name to know! When she walks in a room their is an air about her as everyone wants to know who she is. Her confidence should not be mistaken for conceit. Her spirituality keeps her grounded and her Faith moves mountains. Do you Love Being A Lady? If so this Chic Tee is for you!

100% Baby Rib cotton
Form fitting/Run small
Cap Sleeves
Machine washable
Made in the USA

10% of your order will be donated to the Multiple Sclerosis Society.
